                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-6-victim120 t18260914-6-viclabel28"></join>. On the 4th of September, between five and six o'clock, I was at <placeName id="t18260914-6-crimeloc29">St. Bartholomew fair</placeName>
