                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-6-off25 t18260914-6-crimeloc29"></join>; Cowtan gave me notice that my pocket was picked - he produced my handkerchief, which I had felt safe five minutes before. The prisoner was taken immediately - I had not seen him before.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-6-person121">
                  JOHN 
                  COWTAN
